ygData.messageBody:
Just to let you know : I saw a player (mage type) wielding this kind of
staff, he was kinda high level as he was grouped with rubicite wearing other
ones, druid who was able to teleport the group around (they were at a
druid's ring), etc.

Don't know what this staff was, didn't ask, as I was camoed, running around
them taking screenshots. ;-)

Thormael
